109.movie_plot: After her last encounter, Ellen Ripley crash-lands on Fiorina 161, a maximum security prison. When a series of strange and deadly events occur shortly after her arrival, Ripley realizes that she brought along an unwelcome visitor.

107.movie_plot: A secret agent is sent to Sydney, to find and destroy a genetically modified disease called "Chimera".
